          "doc": "true = Aquarius first (USDC\\xe2\\x86\\x92XLM on Aquarius, XLM\\xe2\\x86\\x92USDC on Sushi).\\nfalse = Sushi first (USDC\\xe2\\x86\\x92XLM on Sushi, XLM\\xe2\\x86\\x92USDC on Aquarius).",
          "name": "aquarius_first",
          "type_": "bool"
        },
        {
          "doc": "",
